CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper April 9, 1960, pg. A2, reads: "Central Baptist Church Plays Host - NAACP Youth Rally Backs Dixie 'Sit-In' War - Singing for Freedom - Among those singing for freedom at the NAACP's youth rally at Central Baptist Church were... The right photo shows Central Baptist's youth choir singing as Leslie Shelton, left, president of the NAACP Youth Council, and Wayne Holt, past president, listen. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: NAACP Youth Council president Leslie Shelton and past president Wayne Holt seated in front of Central Baptist Church youth Choir during NAACP Youth Rally in Central Baptist Church
